$PAR
\((x, y) = \) (\{ans_rule(10)\},\{ans_rule(10)\})

$PAR$HR$PAR
(c) Find the horizontal asymptote for this curve.

$PAR
\(y =\) \{ans_rule(5)\}

$PAR$HR$PAR
(d) Find the vertical asymptote for this curve.

$PAR
\(x =\) \{ans_rule(5)\}

END_TEXT

